author: Kate King
title: SOS Goes Up To Rescue Ship From Scrap Heap of History
text:
CAMDEN, N.J.â€”Preservationists are sounding the alarm about the future of the Barnegat, a historic but dilapidated light ship docked at a private marina here.
Preservation New Jersey, a private nonprofit, is including the Barnegat on its 2018 list of 10 most-endangered historic places in the state with hopes of sparking a grass-roots fundraising...
